message: "If you use this code, please cite it as below."
title: "HLA: Holographic Laplace Attention"
abstract: >
  Decoupling retrieval from content transmission in softmax attention via
  identity-initialized, content-conditioned phase rotation (Q/K),
  bidirectional Laplace gating (K/V), additive salience bias, and
  distance-aware biasing, with a sterile bit-exact comparison harness.
